"The :sub:`($..filter.layerH) no-sub` spacing of the trunks and receptors is "
"set by the spacers. The cable grooves alternate sides on the spacers so that"
" the cables prevent the spacers from moving. The spacers are attached to the"
" trunks and receptors."
